# Operator-local symlinks to sibling Semitexa repositories that are wired in
# as composer path repositories (currently semitexa.pl, which hosts
# semitexa/platform-ui). Each operator runs once:
#   ln -s /absolute/path/to/semitexa.pl ./semitexa.pl
# bin/semitexa autoloads docker-compose.path-repos.yml when this symlink
# exists, mounting it consistently into every container.
/semitexa.pl
